<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6258435e-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s1524"><num value="1524">§ 1524.</num><heading> Rules and regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of the Interior is authorized to prescribe such rules and regulations as may be necessary to carry out the purposes of this chapter.</p>
